nodes.text: Lye-em was an individual who worked as poacher for Rufus Trammel on the moon Dorumaa during the Clone Wars in around 20 BBY. After Trammel's poachers captured the Dorumaan leviathan, Jessel, the poacher Parx asked Lye-em if some of the other poachers were ready to load the creature onto Trammel's starship.
